title: Yu JYUICE 5,000mAh and 10,000mAh power banks launched on Snapdeal, prices start from Rs 699
text: Yu JYUICE 5,000mAh and 10,000mAh power banks launched on Snapdeal, prices start from Rs 699 Sunday, 20 September 2015 (29 minutes ago) After launching the Yunique earlier this month, Yu has now launched new power banks in India. The JYUICE power banks come in 5,000mAh and 10,000mAh capacities, and are priced at Rs 699 and Rs 1,099 respectively. These power banks are exclusive only to Snapdeal and are available in slim grey models. The 5,000mAh is 7.9mm thick and the 10,000mAh is 12.5mm thick. The 5,000mAh has one USB output, while the 10,000mAh offers two micro-USB slots for charging. It comes with multi-color LED lights that are green when the power bank has 70 percent charge, yellow when itâ€™s between 70 and 30 percent, and red when it dips below 30 percent.
